144
00:07:08,300 --> 00:07:10,820
Nowhere. Just wandered around.

145
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:12,660
Alone?

146
00:07:13,860 --> 00:07:14,780
I…

147
00:07:14,780 --> 00:07:15,740
Chen Mo,

148
00:07:16,380 --> 00:07:17,580
don't do this next time.

149
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:20,060
Your mom almost cried,

150
00:07:20,300 --> 00:07:22,260
and mine almost cried too.

151
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:24,260
It's all because my dad hit me!

152
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:26,020
There's a limit to what one can endure!

153
00:07:26,020 --> 00:07:27,340
If he hits me again, I'll…

154
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:28,460
