155
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:30,140
- Your dad hitting you…
- Time to collect homework.

156
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:31,500
Please pass it in.

157
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:35,060
Come on.

158
00:07:40,260 --> 00:07:41,100
Qian Jiayue,

159
00:07:41,380 --> 00:07:42,220
I have a question.

160
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:44,820
Why would you like someone

161
00:07:44,820 --> 00:07:45,900
so different from you?

162
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:47,740
What?

163
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,820
Don't pretend. Ka Men told me everything.

164
00:07:50,620 --> 00:07:51,740
She's such a blabbermouth.

165
00:07:51,910 --> 00:07:53,180
It wasn't just her.

166
00:07:53,180 --> 00:07:54,340
I figured it out myself.

167
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:58,140
But can two people who are so different

168
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,390
really have anything to talk about?

169
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:04,220
I can learn about the things
he likes to talk about.

170
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:07,180
I'd rather he learn about the things
I like to talk about!

171
00:08:07,690 --> 00:08:09,240
- Let me tell you…
- Class is starting.

172
00:08:09,500 --> 00:08:10,700
No more chatting.

173
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:17,480
Hurry up! Class is starting.

174
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,440
- Almost late!
- Hurry!

175
00:08:18,900 --> 00:08:19,740
Alright.

176
00:08:22,210 --> 00:08:23,180
Before we begin,

177
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:24,300
I need to announce something.

178
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:25,820
Wu Zheng

179
00:08:25,820 --> 00:08:26,840
got sick over the weekend,

180
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,740
diagnosed with viral myocarditis.

181
00:08:29,740 --> 00:08:31,460
He's taking a month off.

182
00:08:32,100 --> 00:08:33,900
He's our class's Life Committee Member,

183
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:36,140
so we need someone

184
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:37,460
to fill in temporarily.

185
00:08:37,620 --> 00:08:39,460
According to the last vote,

186
00:08:39,700 --> 00:08:40,700
it should go to

187
00:08:41,180 --> 00:08:42,020
Qian Jiayue.

188
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:43,980
Qian Jiayue,

189
00:08:44,220 --> 00:08:45,140
are you willing?

190
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:46,420
I am.

191
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:48,780
I am willing.

192
00:08:49,300 --> 00:08:50,500
Good. Sit down.

193
00:08:53,060 --> 00:08:53,900
Class.

194
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:54,980
Attention!

195
00:08:55,820 --> 00:08:56,740
Good morning, everyone.

196
00:08:57,500 --> 00:09:00,060
Good morning, teacher.

197
00:09:00,060 --> 00:09:00,900
Please sit down.

198
00:09:10,860 --> 00:09:14,060
♪Is an invisible net♪

199
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:16,580
♪My♪

200
00:09:16,580 --> 00:09:18,300
♪longing♪

201
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:22,660
♪is no longer the sea breaking its banks♪

202
00:09:23,100 --> 00:09:26,540
♪Why do I always♪

203
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:27,700
Mom,

204
00:09:27,820 --> 00:09:29,900
where did you get the karaoke machine?

205
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:31,460
I brought it.

206
00:09:33,180 --> 00:09:34,020
Morning.

207
00:09:35,140 --> 00:09:36,420
Why are you here so early?

208
00:09:36,590 --> 00:09:37,690
Don't you have school today?

209
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:38,740
Baby,

210
00:09:38,940 --> 00:09:40,300
I asked him to come early.

211
00:09:40,340 --> 00:09:41,420
The competition's coming up,

212
00:09:41,420 --> 00:09:42,860
we need to practice.

213
00:09:43,860 --> 00:09:44,740
Honey, honey.

214
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:47,180
Listen to this voice.

215
00:09:47,180 --> 00:09:49,650
Isn't my dad out driving today?

216
00:09:50,500 --> 00:09:51,580
He's not.

217
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:53,520
He specifically took the day off to sing.

218
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:55,140
This couple

219
00:09:55,420 --> 00:09:56,260
is unbelievable.

220
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:57,620
- Unbelievable!
- Look at me.

221
00:09:57,620 --> 00:09:59,420
Why do you always look at the TV?

222
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:00,260
Qian Jiayue,

223
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:01,340
why don't you sing?

224
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:02,540
Why me?

225
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:04,380
- You sing.
- Go sing.

226
00:10:04,380 --> 00:10:05,220
I'll record it.

227
00:10:05,220 --> 00:10:06,340
My dad assigned me this task.

228
00:10:06,890 --> 00:10:07,740
Recording.

229
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:08,860
Rain falling in the heart.

230
00:10:08,860 --> 00:10:10,260
You're making me so nervous.

231
00:10:10,580 --> 00:10:11,420
Chen,

232
00:10:12,020 --> 00:10:15,140
Director Zhao from the neighborhood
committee came yesterday.

233
00:10:16,180 --> 00:10:18,940
She said this is a National Day event,

234
00:10:19,530 --> 00:10:20,940
and since we just moved here,

235
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:22,380
and both you

236
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:24,300
and I are party members,

237
00:10:24,690 --> 00:10:26,590
she hopes we'll lead by example
and participate.

238
00:10:28,740 --> 00:10:30,260
She's already putting pressure on us.

239
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:35,660
You can go if you want,
but I'm not going.

240
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:44,060
Momo, how about

241
00:10:45,260 --> 00:10:46,100
we go together?

242
00:10:47,420 --> 00:10:48,300
Me?

243
00:10:49,610 --> 00:10:50,490
What should I do?

244
00:10:50,490 --> 00:10:52,940
I really don't want to perform.

245
00:10:53,540 --> 00:10:54,380
Then...

246
00:10:54,420 --> 00:10:56,180
let your mom perform alone.

247
00:10:56,180 --> 00:10:57,100
No way.

248
00:10:57,340 --> 00:10:58,540
To be chosen as Model Family,

249
00:10:58,540 --> 00:10:59,820
at least two

250
00:10:59,820 --> 00:11:01,540
family members need to participate.

251
00:11:03,180 --> 00:11:04,580
It's so annoying!

252
00:11:04,580 --> 00:11:05,640
Do you have to perform too?

253
00:11:06,460 --> 00:11:07,540
What are you performing?

254
00:11:07,540 --> 00:11:08,740
With your dad or your mom?

255
00:11:10,060 --> 00:11:11,020
With my dad

256
00:11:11,620 --> 00:11:12,660
and my mom.

257
00:11:14,180 --> 00:11:15,020
Cha-cha!

258
00:11:15,980 --> 00:11:16,820
Rumba!

259
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:19,140
Jitterbug!

260
00:11:19,740 --> 00:11:22,740
Feel the unique Latin vibes!

261
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:27,580
Mine is Chinese traditional culture.

262
00:11:27,860 --> 00:11:29,660
Whether it's the park, the square,

263
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:31,020
or on stage,

264
00:11:31,180 --> 00:11:34,380
I shine brightest!

265
00:11:34,490 --> 00:11:35,380
Tasteless!

266
00:11:35,380 --> 00:11:36,420
Lowlife!

267
00:11:37,980 --> 00:11:39,740
Qing, who will you choose?

268
00:11:40,020 --> 00:11:41,780
So I just had to say,

269
00:11:43,220 --> 00:11:44,220
"You're right.

270
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:46,740
You're right too."

271
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:48,820
So I'm going to dance with

272
00:11:48,820 --> 00:11:50,060
both of them.

273
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,590
Now I feel like my situation
isn't that bad after all.

274
00:11:54,260 --> 00:11:55,100
Brother Xiao Han.

275
00:11:55,540 --> 00:11:56,380
Jiayue.

276
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:57,300
Ka Men.

277
00:11:58,100 --> 00:11:59,220
I'll go with them.

278
00:11:59,580 --> 00:12:00,420
Alright.

279
00:12:00,430 --> 00:12:01,740
- I'll go up first.
- Okay.

280
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:04,740
I heard from my mom that

281
00:12:04,740 --> 00:12:07,380
Xiao Han's family and Mao Tou's family
are teaming up.

282
00:12:07,540 --> 00:12:10,020
Will Xiao Han get on stage and sing?

283
00:12:10,260 --> 00:12:11,420
I've never heard

284
00:12:11,420 --> 00:12:12,580
him sing.

285
00:12:12,580 --> 00:12:13,860
Is he tone-deaf or something?

286
00:12:13,860 --> 00:12:14,700
I don't think so.

287
00:12:14,700 --> 00:12:15,540
He is.

288
00:12:15,580 --> 00:12:16,460
I've heard him.

289
00:12:16,460 --> 00:12:18,240
During flag-raising,
