00:26:06,820 --> 00:26:07,660
Hearts are trump.

573
00:26:07,820 --> 00:26:09,500
Qian Jiayue, if you can beat, beat.

574
00:26:09,500 --> 00:26:10,620
If not, don't add any points!

575
00:26:10,620 --> 00:26:11,460
Got it.

576
00:26:15,620 --> 00:26:16,460
Beat.

577
00:26:16,980 --> 00:26:17,860
Beat again!

578
00:26:18,780 --> 00:26:20,460
We just avoided seventy points!

579
00:26:20,900 --> 00:26:22,700
Qian Jiayue, are you doing this
on purpose?

580
00:26:22,700 --> 00:26:23,860
I told you to beat if you can,

581
00:26:23,860 --> 00:26:25,100
but don't add points if you can't.

582
00:26:25,100 --> 00:26:26,320
You purposely played a pair of kings!

583
00:26:26,320 --> 00:26:28,460
I thought a pair of trump kings
was big enough.

584
00:26:28,620 --> 00:26:29,940
Jiayue just came. Don't blame her.

585
00:26:29,940 --> 00:26:30,820
No internal strife.

586
00:26:31,060 --> 00:26:33,540
Right, you didn't know there was
also a pair of ace of hearts.

587
00:26:34,180 --> 00:26:36,660
Oh my, we're done for.

588
00:26:36,860 --> 00:26:38,060
Look at you, Ka Men.

589
00:26:38,220 --> 00:26:39,380
You always

590
00:26:39,380 --> 00:26:41,180
say we're done for.

591
00:26:41,180 --> 00:26:42,980
Why don't you look at yourself?

592
00:26:43,300 --> 00:26:45,340
Okay, Ka Men, stop complaining.

593
00:26:46,500 --> 00:26:47,700
What else can I do?

594
00:26:48,660 --> 00:26:49,940
Tell me, what else can I do?

595
00:26:50,940 --> 00:26:52,520
Why don't we have Chang Wuji replace you?

596
00:26:52,520 --> 00:26:53,600
You join Qian Jiayue's team.

597
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:55,260
Yeah, Chang Wuji, you play.

598
00:26:55,740 --> 00:26:56,740
What game are we playing?

599
00:26:56,740 --> 00:26:58,060
80 points. Can you play?

600
00:26:59,700 --> 00:27:00,940
- I know a little.
- Come on.

601
00:27:00,940 --> 00:27:02,030
Chang Wuji, think carefully.

602
00:27:02,220 --> 00:27:03,980
Chen Mo and I are already at J.

603
00:27:03,980 --> 00:27:05,900
Are you sure you can handle this?

604
00:27:07,700 --> 00:27:08,700
What are the rules again?

605
00:27:12,300 --> 00:27:13,940
No worries, I'll explain.

606
00:27:14,100 --> 00:27:15,380
Yeah, it's simple.

607
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:20,020
All clubs.

608
00:27:20,980 --> 00:27:22,700
Xiao Han, you still have some clubs.

609
00:27:23,100 --> 00:27:24,420
All the points you left are ours.

610
00:27:25,500 --> 00:27:26,340
Chen Mo,

611
00:27:26,540 --> 00:27:28,030
your trump is not enough,
you can't beat me.

612
00:27:28,500 --> 00:27:29,340
Show your cards.

613
00:27:29,860 --> 00:27:30,700
Jiayue has 20 points.

614
00:27:31,460 --> 00:27:32,300
Shuffle.

615
00:27:32,700 --> 00:27:33,540
We're at 4.

616
00:27:33,860 --> 00:27:34,740
Pretty good.

617
00:27:35,180 --> 00:27:36,100
Fast learner.

618
00:27:36,540 --> 00:27:37,660
It's okay, we're still at J.

619
00:27:39,100 --> 00:27:41,540
Xiao Han, your third round ace
is already played.

620
00:27:41,700 --> 00:27:43,420
The only ace left is with Jiayue.

621
00:27:44,140 --> 00:27:46,100
Chen Mo, you have one
ten of diamonds left.

622
00:27:46,100 --> 00:27:47,340
Play it, I'll play the king.

623
00:27:53,300 --> 00:27:54,660
Jiayue, we're at 7.

624
00:27:56,260 --> 00:27:57,500
It's okay, we're still at J.

625
00:27:57,900 --> 00:27:58,740
Come on.

626
00:28:00,260 --> 00:28:01,180
Show the cards.

627
00:28:01,180 --> 00:28:02,260
You've got forty points.

628
00:28:02,260 --> 00:28:03,100
We're at K.

629
00:28:03,860 --> 00:28:05,860
Awesome, Chang Wuji!

630
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:07,140
Are you a genius or what?

631
00:28:07,140 --> 00:28:08,900
How do you remember all the cards?

632
00:28:10,060 --> 00:28:11,060
Do you have any tricks?

633
00:28:11,060 --> 00:28:11,980
Teach me!

634
00:28:13,290 --> 00:28:14,380
- Finished yet?
- Finished!

635
00:28:16,640 --> 00:28:17,590
Look at this big turtle.

636
00:28:20,340 --> 00:28:21,180
Brother Xiao Han!

637
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:23,240
It must be the first time you've had
a turtle drawn on your face!

638
00:28:23,780 --> 00:28:25,940
I've never seen Xiao Han
like this before.

639
00:28:26,100 --> 00:28:27,900
Xiao Han, this big turtle!

640
00:28:27,900 --> 00:28:29,660
You're the turtle!
You've got two turtles!

641
00:28:29,660 --> 00:28:30,500
Look at mine.

642
00:28:30,500 --> 00:28:32,390
If you didn't know,
you'd think they were moles!

643
00:28:32,690 --> 00:28:33,540
Are you saying

644
00:28:33,540 --> 00:28:34,700
I didn't draw them well?

645
00:28:34,900 --> 00:28:36,740
Seriously, look at his.

646
00:28:36,740 --> 00:28:38,620
No, I'll add two more strokes for you.

647
00:28:39,170 --> 00:28:40,260
Let me add two more strokes.

648
00:28:40,260 --> 00:28:41,100
Add?

649
00:28:41,100 --> 00:28:42,780
You can't add anymore! No more!

650
00:28:54,340 --> 00:28:58,980
♪Youth is like a pair of footsteps♪

651
00:29:01,020 --> 00:29:06,200
♪Innocently measuring the dream♪

652
00:29:06,970 --> 00:29:10,480
♪Over mountains, past obstacles♪

653
00:29:10,950 --> 00:29:13,800
♪See if the world♪

654
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:19,510
♪Feels like a theme park♪

655
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:24,010
♪The future has countless different looks♪

656
00:29:24,140 --> 00:29:25,140
Let's take a group photo!

657
00:29:25,380 --> 00:29:26,500
Come on!

658
00:29:27,260 --> 00:29:28,100
Look at me!

659
00:29:28,110 --> 00:29:29,380
Three, two, one!

660
00:29:29,780 --> 00:29:31,500
Smile, cheese!

661
00:29:33,910 --> 00:29:37,420
♪Sometimes short, sometimes long♪

662
00:29:39,460 --> 00:29:40,660
This is so spectacular.

663
00:29:42,260 --> 00:29:43,700
They're really so coordinated.

664
00:29:43,840 --> 00:29:45,640
Watching this makes me
want to join the army.

665
00:29:46,840 --> 00:29:47,700
Look, female soldiers!

666
00:29:48,300 --> 00:29:50,380
So this is Chang'an Avenue.

667
00:29:50,690 --> 00:29:51,900
Beijing's sky is so blue,

668
00:29:51,900 --> 00:29:52,740
and the road is wide.

669
00:29:52,740 --> 00:29:54,260
I really want to go to Beijing!

670
00:29:54,460 --> 00:29:55,580
I want to go too!

671
00:29:55,580 --> 00:29:56,820
Let's go together in the future.

672
00:29:59,020 --> 00:29:59,860
Qian Jiayue,

673
00:30:00,260 --> 00:30:01,860
what are you writing?

674
00:30:02,320 --> 00:30:03,760
I'm writing down the narration.

675
00:30:04,720 --> 00:30:06,360
What for?

676
00:30:06,390 --> 00:30:08,140
I'm going to use it
in my composition later.

677
00:30:08,620 --> 00:30:10,440
Did the teacher tell us
to write compositions?

678
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:11,800
No.

679
00:30:11,820 --> 00:30:12,860
I'm writing it myself.

680
00:30:17,140 --> 00:30:19,340
Their steps are incredibly synchronized.

681
00:30:22,700 --> 00:30:23,580
Hurry up, you two!

682
00:30:23,740 --> 00:30:26,940
Let's warm up
before Liu Jianfeng arrives.

683
00:30:27,140 --> 00:30:28,600
- Bye, Chen Mo!
- Take care!

684
00:30:29,860 --> 00:30:30,740
Brother Xiao Han,

685
00:30:31,100 --> 00:30:32,780
after your game, I'll look for you.

686
00:30:32,780 --> 00:30:34,060
I've got something for you.

687
00:30:34,300 --> 00:30:35,140
Sure.

688
00:30:35,260 --> 00:30:36,140
We're heading out now.

689
00:30:37,380 --> 00:30:38,340
Thanks for having us.

690
00:30:38,340 --> 00:30:39,700
No problem! Come again soon!

691
00:30:39,980 --> 00:30:41,300
- Bye.
- See you later!

692
00:30:44,540 --> 00:30:47,180
Everything was perfect today
except the card game.

693
00:30:48,340 --> 00:30:49,180
Chang Wuji,

694
00:30:49,340 --> 00:30:50,740
you were amazing earlier,

695
00:30:50,740 --> 00:30:52,940
like a legendary martial arts master
from a novel.

696
00:30:53,170 --> 00:30:54,060
Thanks.

697
00:30:55,730 --> 00:30:56,570
Chang Wuji,

698
00:30:56,790 --> 00:30:58,190
why don't you walk Qian Jiayue home?

699
00:31:00,180 --> 00:31:01,020
No need.

700
00:31:01,100 --> 00:31:02,180
Workers' New Village is just

701
00:31:02,180 --> 00:31:03,340
across the street.

702
00:31:03,740 --> 00:31:05,190
Crossing the street can be dangerous.

703
00:31:06,160 --> 00:31:08,180
Actually, traffic accidents in Shanghai

704
00:31:08,180 --> 00:31:09,390
have decreased in recent years.

705
00:31:09,540 --> 00:31:10,780
Most accidents

706
00:31:10,780 --> 00:31:12,940
involve vehicles,

707
00:31:13,140 --> 00:31:14,660
not pedestrians.

708
00:31:14,860 --> 00:31:16,740
As long as you walk properly…

709
00:31:16,900 --> 00:31:19,540
Excuse me. It's really unnecessary.

710
00:31:20,060 --> 00:31:20,900
Really.

711
00:31:21,180 --> 00:31:22,100
I agree.

712
00:31:23,180 --> 00:31:24,060
I agree too.

713
00:31:24,790 --> 00:31:25,630
Bye.

714
00:31:26,060 --> 00:31:27,100
Bye. See you at school.

715
00:31:27,210 --> 00:31:28,080
See you.

716
00:31:28,100 --> 00:31:28,940
We're leaving too.

717
00:31:29,220 --> 00:31:30,240
- Leaving.
- Walk safely.

718
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:31,090
- Happy Holiday!
- Bye.

719
00:31:31,090 --> 00:31:32,500
- Happy Holiday!
- See you at Xidian Mall!

720
00:31:32,500 --> 00:31:35,220
(Puyang New Village)

721
00:31:47,460 --> 00:31:48,300
Brother Xiao Han,

722
00:31:49,060 --> 00:31:50,100
come here.

723
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:50,940
What?

724
00:31:51,700 --> 00:31:54,820
Brother Bin lent me
the tape of "Fight Back to School".

725
00:31:54,900 --> 00:31:56,180
He said it's really good

726
00:31:56,180 --> 00:31:57,860
and that there's a surprise.

727
00:31:58,540 --> 00:31:59,940
But have you finished your homework?

728
00:31:59,980 --> 00:32:01,100
Don't spoil the fun!

729
00:32:01,100 --> 00:32:02,500
It's the first day of the holiday,

730
00:32:02,500 --> 00:32:03,810
there's plenty of time ahead.

731
00:32:21,100 --> 00:32:23,380
- Without it, it will…
- It's very dangerous.

732
00:32:32,980 --> 00:32:33,820
What?

733
00:32:33,980 --> 00:32:34,820
What's going on?

734
00:32:36,260 --> 00:32:37,660
It's probably a very old tape.

735
00:32:38,100 --> 00:32:39,100
Is it erased?

736
00:32:40,180 --> 00:32:41,020
I don't know.

737
00:32:45,500 --> 00:32:47,300
What... What is this?

738
00:32:48,990 --> 00:32:50,020
Mao Tou, stop watching it.

739
00:32:50,020 --> 00:32:51,420
Quick, turn it off!

740
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:54,180
Soon... Soon...

741
00:32:54,180 --> 00:32:56,300
Soon... Soon, it'll come back.

742
00:32:59,500 --> 00:33:00,580
I see you're not

743
00:33:00,580 --> 00:33:02,060
very happy with playing Yang Bailao.

744
00:33:03,100 --> 00:33:03,940
Yongqiang's dad.

745
00:33:04,700 --> 00:33:06,460
I originally wanted to use this chance

746
00:33:06,460 --> 00:33:08,540
to show everyone our emotions,

747
00:33:08,540 --> 00:33:09,500
but it turned into showcasing

748
00:33:09,500 --> 00:33:11,280
the relationship
between Yang Bailao and his daughter.

749
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:12,740
The idea completely went sideways.

750
00:33:13,940 --> 00:33:15,100
I didn't think that much.

751
00:33:15,460 --> 00:33:17,060
Do you know why I chose this piece?

752
00:33:17,300 --> 00:33:18,140
Why?

753
00:33:19,560 --> 00:33:20,860
When I hear this music,

754
00:33:21,300 --> 00:33:23,540
I think of the lively days
at No. 9 Factory.

755
00:33:26,460 --> 00:33:28,300
The first time you sang "Red Yarn"

756
00:33:28,660 --> 00:33:30,700
was at our factory's

757
00:33:31,940 --> 00:33:32,940
National Day party.

758
00:33:33,060 --> 00:33:34,980
I was in the audience, almost drooling.

759
00:33:35,240 --> 00:33:36,140
I get it now. I promise

760
00:33:36,140 --> 00:33:37,460
I'll perform Yang Bailao well.

761
00:33:38,140 --> 00:33:40,580
I prepared a piece of red yarn.

762
00:33:40,580 --> 00:33:43,220
To tie my daughter's plait.

763
00:33:43,380 --> 00:33:44,940
To tie your plait.

764
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:46,860
You need to practice more.

765
00:33:46,860 --> 00:33:48,060
Others do it like butterflies,

766
00:33:48,060 --> 00:33:49,060
but yours look like...

767
00:33:49,460 --> 00:33:50,300
grasshoppers!

768
00:33:51,100 --> 00:33:52,180
Grasshoppers? Well…

769
00:33:55,500 --> 00:33:56,340
Is Han at home?

770
00:33:57,580 --> 00:33:58,740
- He's not here.
- Come on!

771
00:33:58,740 --> 00:33:59,580
Take it!

772
00:33:59,580 --> 00:34:00,420
Why me?

773
00:34:00,420 --> 00:34:01,260
- No way!
- Han?

774
00:34:01,420 --> 00:34:02,260
Han?

775
00:34:02,860 --> 00:34:03,700
Han?

776
00:34:09,220 --> 00:34:10,060
Han?

777
00:34:11,380 --> 00:34:12,220
Han?

778
00:34:18,700 --> 00:34:19,700
I told you,

779
00:34:19,700 --> 00:34:20,580
he's not here.

780
00:34:21,340 --> 00:34:22,580
Didn't they agree to

781
00:34:22,580 --> 00:34:24,540
go to a classmate's home
to watch the parade?

782
00:34:24,540 --> 00:34:26,540
I clearly heard a voice just now.

783
00:34:27,180 --> 00:34:28,820
You're exhausted, you're hearing things.

784
00:34:28,940 --> 00:34:30,220
Let me get you some water.

785
00:34:35,380 --> 00:34:36,220
Aiping,

786
00:34:36,700 --> 00:34:39,340
the kids are really supportive
of us participating

787
00:34:39,780 --> 00:34:41,780
in the Model Family event.

788
00:34:42,340 --> 00:34:43,180
About...

789
00:34:43,620 --> 00:34:44,660
us...

790
00:34:45,140 --> 00:34:47,020
can you give me clear instructions?

791
00:34:48,120 --> 00:34:49,740
Mao Tou has the High School Entrance Exam.

792
00:34:49,830 --> 00:34:50,700
Han is

793
00:34:50,700 --> 00:34:52,060
stressed with high school.

794
00:34:52,980 --> 00:34:54,420
Is that clear enough?

795
00:34:55,940 --> 00:34:56,780
Clear.

796
00:34:56,820 --> 00:34:58,340
Clear enough for three years ahead.

797
00:34:59,420 --> 00:35:02,580
High school and college entrance exams
are important,

798
00:35:05,140 --> 00:35:06,700
but I was thinking...

799
00:35:08,340 --> 00:35:09,180
in fact,

800
00:35:09,660 --> 00:35:11,220
we should tell the kids

801
00:35:11,620 --> 00:35:12,980
sooner.

802
00:35:13,140 --> 00:35:13,980
That way,

803
00:35:14,040 --> 00:35:16,420
I can take better care of you both.

804
00:35:16,900 --> 00:35:18,140
Right? You see,

805
00:35:18,140 --> 00:35:19,380
you don't take my money,

806
00:35:19,820 --> 00:35:21,180
but work so hard every day.

807
00:35:21,180 --> 00:35:22,020
No matter,

808
00:35:22,030 --> 00:35:23,940
I really feel for you.

809
00:35:31,220 --> 00:35:32,500
But I really don't know

810
00:35:32,740 --> 00:35:34,180
how to bring it up with Han.

811
00:35:35,220 --> 00:35:36,060
And...

812
00:35:41,980 --> 00:35:43,140
actually, I haven't

813
00:35:43,620 --> 00:35:45,180
thought through a lot of things.

814
00:35:46,340 --> 00:35:47,220
Don't push me.

815
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:48,980
No, no,

816
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:50,140
I definitely didn't mean that.

817
00:35:50,220 --> 00:35:51,180
Definitely not.

818
00:35:52,380 --> 00:35:53,620
Sometimes, dealing with kids

819
00:35:53,620 --> 00:35:54,900
really feels like a war.

820
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:57,340
An outflanking war.

821
00:35:57,900 --> 00:35:58,740
A protracted war.

822
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:01,100
I need to study "The Art of War" again.

823
00:36:02,380 --> 00:36:03,220
No problem.

824
00:36:03,740 --> 00:36:05,140
As for the Model Family competition,

825
00:36:05,260 --> 00:36:06,580
I'll do my best and try to

826
00:36:06,820 --> 00:36:08,700
leave a good impression on Han.

827
00:36:09,980 --> 00:36:11,300
Not just Han.

828
00:36:11,500 --> 00:36:12,580
Don't forget about Mao Tou.

829
00:36:12,820 --> 00:36:13,940
What will Mao Tou think?

830
00:36:14,190 --> 00:36:15,740
He definitely won't have any objections!

831
00:36:16,020 --> 00:36:17,700
I guarantee it.

832
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:19,580
He must have no objections.

833
00:36:19,940 --> 00:36:20,820
Rest assured.

834
00:36:20,980 --> 00:36:22,020
I'm telling you,

835
00:36:22,020 --> 00:36:24,380
don't always be so rough on Mao Tou.

836
00:36:24,580 --> 00:36:25,500
Okay, okay.

837
00:36:25,500 --> 00:36:27,380
Everything you say, I'll take it to heart

838
00:36:27,870 --> 00:36:29,100
and slowly change.

839
00:36:31,940 --> 00:36:34,460
Qiming, smoke on the balcony.

840
00:36:34,900 --> 00:36:37,020
Han doesn't like the smell of smoke
in the room.

841
00:36:40,220 --> 00:36:41,740
I can hold it for three years,

842
00:36:41,740 --> 00:36:42,940
but I can't hold back one cigarette?

843
00:36:42,940 --> 00:36:44,540
Are you kidding?

844
00:36:44,540 --> 00:36:45,380
I won't smoke.

845
00:36:45,380 --> 00:36:46,220
It's fine.

846
00:36:46,820 --> 00:36:47,660
Since

847
00:36:48,820 --> 00:36:50,140
the little ones aren't here,

848
00:36:50,790 --> 00:36:51,990
we don't have to cook for them.

849
00:36:52,420 --> 00:36:53,260
Right?

850
00:36:53,260 --> 00:36:54,940
Let's go to Nanjing Road,

851
00:36:55,220 --> 00:36:56,500
I'll buy you some new outfits

852
00:36:57,060 --> 00:36:59,140
